Publish an article

Usage: mf article publish [OPTIONS] <ID_OR_PATH>

Arguments:
  <ID_OR_PATH>  

Options:
      --config <PATH>    
      --target <TARGET>  
      --dry-run          
  -v, --verbose...       
      --force            
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
